<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>New Booking Request</title></head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; color: #333;">
  <h1 style="color: #2563eb;">New booking request</h1>
  <p>You have a new booking request for <strong>{{listingTitle}}</strong>.</p>
  <p>Please review and confirm or decline the request in your provider dashboard.</p>
  <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingId}}" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:16px;padding:12px 24px;background:#2563eb;color:#fff;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Review Request</a>
  <hr style="margin-top:32px;border:none;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;">
  <p style="font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af;">Relocation Platform — find your home abroad</p>
</body>
</html>
